      "heading": "Detailed description",
      "text": "The MikroTik RB4011 Wall Mount Kit (WMK4011) is a reliable and practical solution for securely mounting your RB4011 router on a wall while protecting it from unauthorized access. Made from high-quality steel, this mount offers excellent durability and stability, ensuring your device stays safely in place. The design allows you to plug in Ethernet cables before installing the router into the mount — once secured, the cables cannot be easily unplugged or tampered with. This makes the WMK4011 especially useful in offices, public spaces, or shared environments where network equipment needs extra protection. The solid metal construction guarantees long-term use, while the clean and professional look fits seamlessly into any setup. Combining safety, functionality, and convenience, the RB4011 Wall Mount Kit provides a simple and effective way to organize and secure your MikroTik router in any workspace."
    }
